Gordon Harris (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gordon_Harris_(actor) 0 Jamie Harris (born 15 May 1963) is a British actor. He is best known for his role as The Hook-Handed Man in Lemony Snicket's A Series of Unfortunate Events, Rodney in Rise of the Planet of the Apes and Gordon in Marvel's Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D..
